title: [Arboretum]
description: A well dressed but well armed guard stands before a pair of elegant wooden doors, one trimmed in gold and the other colorfully painted.  He bears a friendly expression on his face, but his eyes remain vigilant and alert.  A gleaming silver sign hangs between the doors.
